page1.title: About Me
page1.content: 👋🏻 I’m Aniket, a software engineer who loves to tinker. . 🔨 Currently, I am working as a machine learning engineer in Accenture building a search product for healthcare enterprises. I am also into web development, actively learning and building apps. In the past, I have integrated features based on ML into web apps built using react. I have interests in NLP and next generation web apps. . 🧬 Besides day to day work, I read a lot. Currently, I am reading 📚 Susan Cain’s Quiet. . 💸 I love discussing about technology, cryptocurrency and investing or any random facts. . ✉️ You can email me at email or reach out to me on twitter or at linkedin .
